portunities. ... And be a member of the team.', 48333, 0), (418836, 'Vacillating people seldom succeed. They seldom win the solid respect of their fellows. Successful men and women are very careful in reaching decisions  and very persistent and determined in action thereafter.', 65840, 0), (418837, 'Many people have the ambition to succeed  they may even have a special aptitude for their job. And yet they do not move ahead. Why? Perhaps they think that since they can master the job  there is no need to master themselves.', 18124, 0), (418838, 'I''ve been polite and I''ve always shown up. Somebody asked me if I had any advice for young people entering the business. I said: "Yeah  show up."', 65841, 0), (418839, 'The wise man puts all his eggs in one basket and watches the basket.', 4963, 0), (418840, 'I know the price of success: dedication  hard work and an unremitting devotion to the things you want to see happen.', 1836, 0), (418841, 'Success is that old ABC-Ability  Breaks and Courage.', 11189, 0), (418842, 'The secret of success in life is for a man to be ready for his opportunity when it comes.', 1827, 0), (418843, 'If one advances confidently in the direction of his dreams  and endeavors to live the life which he has imaged  he will meet with success unexpected in common hours.', 1049, 0), (418844, 'Before everything else  getting ready is the secret of success.', 1796, 0), (418845, 'To be ambitious for wealth  and yet always expecting to be poor  to be always doubting your ability to get what you long for  is like trying to reach east by traveling west. There is no philosophy which will help man to succeed when he is always doubting his ability to do so  and thus attracting failure. No matter how hard you work for success  if your thought is saturated with the fear of failure  it will kill your efforts  neutralize your endeavors and make success impossible.', 62516, 0), (418846, 'I cannot give you the formula for success  but I can give you the formula for failure  which is-try to please everybody.', 1676, 0), (418847, 'We may fail of our happiness  strive we ever so bravely  but we are less likely to fail if we measure with judgement our chances and our capabilities.', 24996, 0), (418848, 'A double-minded man is unstable in all his ways.... A determinate purpose in life and a steady adhesion to it through all disadvantages are indispensable conditions of success.', 64000, 0), (418849, 'The conditions of conquest are always easy. We have but to toil awhile  endure awhile  believe always  and never turn back.', 62237, 0), (418850, 'The very first step towards success in any occupation is to become interested in it.', 63225, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (418851, 'I studied the lives of great men and famous women  and I found that the men and women who got to the top were those who did the jobs they had in hand  with everything they had of energy and enthusiasm and hard work.', 16121, 0), (418852, 'Without ambition one starts nothing. Without work one finishes nothing. The prize will not be sent to you. As to methods there may be a million and then some  but the principles are few. The man who grasps principles can successfully select his own methods. The man who tries methods  ignoring principles  is sure to have trouble.', 760, 0), (418853, 'There are no secrets to success. It is the result of preparation  hard work  learning from failure.', 65842, 0), (418854, 'Success is blocked by concentrating on it and planning for it.... Success is shy-it won''t come out while you''re watching.', 355, 0), (418855, 'Three outstanding qualities make for success: judgement  industry  health. And the greatest of these is judgement.', 65843, 0), (418856, 'Thirteen virtues necessary for true success: temperance  silence  order  resolution  frugality  industry  sincerity  justice  moderation  cleanliness  tranquility  chastity  and humility.', 1077, 0), (418857, 'Find a need and fill it.', 65352, 0), (418858, 'Put your heart  mind  intellect and soul even to your smallest acts. This is the secret of success.', 62960, 0), (418859, 'Four steps to achievement: plan purposefully  prepare prayerfully  proceed positively  pursue persistently.', 62349, 0), (418860, 'Success follows doing what you want to do. There is no other way to be successful.', 5930, 0), (418861, 'Always aim for achievement  and forget about success.', 4743, 0), (418862, 'Success  which is something so simple in the end  is made up of thousands of things  we never fully know what.', 36, 0), (418863, 'Self-trust is the first secret of success.', 760, 0), (418864, 'The man who will use his skill and constructive