ard ratio is right  you can make big money buying trouble.', 33, 0), (418933, 'What isn''t tried won''t work.', 65543, 0), (418934, 'He that is overcautious will accomplish little.', 62240, 0), (418935, 'All great reforms require one to dare a lot to win a little.', 65545, 0), (418936, 'If you limit your actions in life to things that nobody can possibly find fault with  you will not do much.', 65546, 0), (418937, 'The ambitious climbs high and perilous stairs and never cares how to come down  the desire of rising hath swallowed up his fear of a fall.', 62521, 0), (418938, 'He that would have fruit must climb the tree.', 1348, 0), (418939, 'To get profit without risk  experience without danger and reward without work is as impossible as it is to live without being born.', 65548, 0), (418940, 'Every noble acquisition is attended with its risks  he who fears to encounter the one must not expect to obtain the other.', 62993, 0), (418941, 'The method of the enterprising is to plan with audacity and execute with vigor.', 7233, 0), (418942, 'Great deeds are usually wrought at great risks.', 1863, 0), (418943, 'Only those who dare to fail greatly can ever achieve greatly.', 1973, 0), (418944, 'No one reaches a high position without daring.', 2904, 0), (418945, 'Cadillacs are down at the end of the bat.', 65549, 0), (418946, 'It is impossible to win the great prizes of life without running risks.', 1674, 0), (418947, 'You can''t expect to hit the jackpot if you don''t put a few nickels in the machine.', 40017, 0), (418948, 'Who dares nothing  need hope for nothing.', 62240, 0), (418949, 'Progress always involves risks. You can''t steal second base and keep your foot on first.', 65550, 0), (418950, 'I don''t think about risks much. I just do what I want to do. If you gotta go  you gotta go.', 63321, 0);
